node.title: Footage shows man deliberately shoving woman in front of train
node.description: The 23-year-old suspect has been arrested on charges of attempted manslaughter.
node.content: ["Shocking CCTV footage has emerged online showing a man forcefully pushing a woman off a train platform into the path of an oncoming train.\u00a0", "The footage recorded in Brussels shows a man sneaking up behind a woman, who was waiting for her train to arrive before he shoved her onto the train tracks, falling face first.\u00a0", "An oncoming train came to a halt only missing the woman by meters.", "Police told Breaking911 the suspect was a 23-year-old who was arrested on charges of attempted manslaughter.\u00a0", "It's unclear whether the 55-year-old woman suffered serious injuries."]
